{"tid":874627,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拿假貨辦展覽 草間彌生、村上隆擬控告中國展方","createTime":"2018-10-24T10:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T10:58:11.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"684139685d69ab91726cd097a035c8bf83e91575","tid":874627,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phprU5VNI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phprU5VNI.jpg&h=0cd17e9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作品在中國遭侵權，草間彌生擬對中國展方提出刑事訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國屢發生侵權事件，日媒今（24）日獲悉，有中國展方打著享譽全球的日本現代藝術家草間彌生和村上隆旗號，在中國各地舉辦展覽，展出大量贗品。草間彌生和村上隆擬對中國展方提出刑事訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n日經中文網報導，草間彌生的代理律師小野寺良文表示，這場假展覽今年4月以來至少已在深圳、廣州、武漢及上海舉辦。展名為「草間彌生&times;村上隆藏品雙聯展」，展出大量冒充「波點女王」草間作品的繪畫和雕塑等，只有上海的展覽需要買票，單人票60元人民幣（約新台幣267元），親子票（1大人1小孩）100元人民幣（約新台幣445元）。<br />\n<br />\n但草間彌生和村上隆都未參與這些展出作品的創作，作品被認為是贗品。草間和村上二人均主張「此舉侵犯了自身的著作權並違反中國法律」，討論對展覽策劃公司提起刑事訴訟等。<br />\n<br />\n草間方面認為，中國展方擅自在各會場型展覽，針對9月中旬開始的上海展，已經向會場方面寄送了警告書，迫使展覽中止，計劃調查實際情況，確定責任者後，將從刑事和民事層面推進法律程序。村上的代理律師上山浩也表示，「性質十分惡劣，討論採取同樣的應對措施」。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，在中國，日本動漫的山寨作品橫行，日本企業等的著作權和商標，其智慧財產權被侵犯的情況屢見不鮮，制定應對措施成為當務之急。報導稱，這次中國擅自舉辦「虛假展覽」的做法十分大膽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpo0URoC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpo0URoC.jpg&h=127e1f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n村上隆（圖）的代理律師上山浩也表示，「性質十分惡劣，討論採取同樣的應對措施」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpCrW9V2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpCrW9V2.jpg&h=74e165ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國舉行「草間彌生&times;村上隆藏品雙聯展」，展出大量冒充「波點女王」草間作品的繪畫和雕塑等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2590838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2590838&d=oV03Jz3tVDaVEDGqvmAcKGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=a8ada69f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2590838&h=b111bc57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2590838</a>"},{"pid":"a500f81809994fbe1cee8b63c1e05377cc7326c9","tid":874627,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:37:23.000Z","msg":"咩都可以假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n琴日開通儀式有冇假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64147ee9335b402ae4dcf75238cdda032f035f2","tid":874627,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a500f81809994fbe1cee8b63c1e05377cc7326c9","tid":874627,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:37:23.000Z","msg":"咩都可以假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n琴日開通儀式有冇假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:44:18.000Z","msg":"個維尼假架"},{"pid":"30aafc4a894dd7ed4899b5a9c5c7866c4295dc6d","tid":874627,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:45:07.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"f47675c934cf231827a9642cf7a4e09920b1dc96","tid":874627,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:51:07.000Z","msg":"cls呢的展覽都假 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e400875000322a8323968d07509039a2ed9139","tid":874627,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a500f81809994fbe1cee8b63c1e05377cc7326c9","tid":874627,"uid":141151,"like